      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>You swiftly pursue fleeing foes.</p>\n<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Dex 17, base attack bonus +10, @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.feats.Item.wn1sqrolPngpe7G9]{Step Up}, @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.feats.Item.xCzcnmvztoWLlqbe]{Step Up and Strike}</p><hr /><p><strong>Benefit:</strong> When using the Step Up and Strike feat to follow an adjacent foe, you can move up to 30 feet, though you can never move more than 10 feet per attack of opportunity that the foe provokes. If you make an attack of opportunity against the foe, you may attempt a @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.rules.JournalEntry.U37n5tY5hn1ctzQL.JournalEntryPage.R33uiOMesYP0ISWl#combat-maneuver]{combat maneuver} in place of the normal melee attack; if you do, you get a +2 bonus to the attempt.</p>"
